title: Dungeon Pass error
body: I bought the dungeon pass and only received the 10 good orbs.  I didn't get the icon, gemstone or the mission lines.  What do I do to get these?

replies.body: I've gone ahead and checked your purchase history, and I only see where you bought the pack of 10 Good Orbs + 1 Bonus Orb. I'm not seeing anywhere that this account has bought either of the passes, but let me know if you were talking about a different account and I can check that one as well!
Have you tried restarting your client? Sometimes things don't appear right away.
Yeah, it's been a couple of days since I bought the pass.  Still nothing.
